sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as Context Manager
    participant A as AI Agent (LLM)
    participant F as Filter Engine
    participant D as Product Database

    U->>C: "I need a sofa for my living room"
    C->>C: Store message in session history
    C->>A: Send full chat history + new message
    A->>A: Extract: room=living_room, type=sofa
    A->>F: Filter(room=living_room, type=sofa)
    F->>D: Query DataFrame
    D-->>F: 45 matching products
    F-->>A: Top 5 ranked results
    A-->>C: Response + products
    C->>C: Store assistant response in history
    C-->>U: "Here are 5 sofas for your living room..."

    U->>C: "Under 30000 budget"
    C->>C: Append to history
    C->>A: Full history (includes prior context)
    A->>A: Merge context: room=living_room, type=sofa, budget_max=30000
    A->>F: Filter(room=living_room, type=sofa, budget≤30000)
    F->>D: Query with accumulated filters
    D-->>F: 12 matching products
    F-->>A: Top 5 ranked results
    A-->>C: Refined response + products
    C-->>U: "Here are sofas under ₹30,000..."

    U->>C: "Show me in warm colors"
    C->>C: Append to history
    C->>A: Full history (all prior context preserved)
    A->>A: Merge: room=living, type=sofa, budget≤30k, color=warm
    A->>F: Filter with all accumulated criteria
    F-->>A: Top matches
    A-->>C: Further refined results
    C-->>U: "Warm-toned sofas under ₹30,000..."
